From 74f5bdd3eb41e093e88114e932eadd6ea858ac0e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Kenvish Butani <kbutani@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Tue, 17 Jun 2025 22:37:29 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM: DP: wifi: ath12k: Add Telemetry counter in Rx REO
 Path

- Introduced support for telemetry counters at the
  Link Peer level in the per-packet Rx REO path.
- Added both Debug and Advanced counters to
  enhance packet tracking during Rx.
- Enhanced all packet drop conditions with
  device-level stats counters to capture every
  packet drop event.

Command to enable:
echo 1 > /sys/kernel/debug/ath12k/pci-XX/macX/enable_dp_stats
echo 1 > /sys/kernel/debug/ath12k/pci-XX/macX/enable_dp_debug_stats

Sample Output:
STA DP RX STATS
================
        Received from reo-packets       40
        Sent to stack-packets           40
        Sent to stack-bytes             4544
        non amsdu                       18
        msdu part of amsdu              22
        mpdu retry                      0

RX WBM ERROR:
--------------
        RXDMA ERROR:    0       0       0       0       0
        REO ERROR:      0       0       0       0       0
--------------

Patch-dependency:
	0426-0006-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Mcast-Stats-in-Tx-path.patch

Signed-off-by: Kenvish Butani <kbutani@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
